"Generate the summary using HTML tags only.
Use <strong> for bold text.
Use <ul> and <li> for bullet points.
For the Contact Name and any related records, you must include a link using this exact syntax: <a href="/RECORD_ID_HERE">RECORD_NAME_HERE</a>.
Important: Do not use Markdown (no ** or #)."


